CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 8, 1961, pg. 22 reads: "Broke Even - This second volley ball cast, of Ammon Recreation Center, broke even in four games during the recent city championship tournament at the South Side Field House. Left to right: Connie Davison, Marion Smith, Yvonne Hill, Betty Brady, Gloria Wilson and Capt. Eula Thompson. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ammon Center volleyball team, from left: Connie Davison, Marion Smith, Yvonne Hill, Betty Brady, Gloria Wilson, and Capt. Eula Thompson, standing in Ammon Center
